author: @agentNirmites
text: Check it out ---  import gym import time  env = gym.make('MountainCar-v0') env.reset()  done = False previous_state = [0, 0] action = 2 while not done:     # action 0 => push the car left     # action 1 => do nothing     # action 2 => push the car right      new_state, reward, done, _ = env.step(action)     if previous_state[0] > new_state[0]:         action = 0     if previous_state[0] < new_state[0]:         action = 2     previous_state = new_state[:]     env.render()     time.sleep(0.1)  env.close()
